  "lyrics": [
    {
      "time": 19.38,
      "time_str": "00:19.380",
      "text": "原谅我真的喝醉了",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 23.14,
      "time_str": "00:23.140",
      "text": "因为我真的想你了",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 26.76,
      "time_str": "00:26.760",
      "text": "一不小心就被寂寞吞噬了爱着你的快乐",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 34.11,
      "time_str": "00:34.110",
      "text": "我知道这样不应该也知道你会受伤害",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 41.38,
      "time_str": "00:41.380",
      "text": "只是不想再让自己对你太过依赖",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 48.48,
      "time_str": "00:48.480",
      "text": "我明白 你给的爱 是真实地存在",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 55.92,
      "time_str": "00:55.920",
      "text": "只是我 不懂得如何去爱",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 61.68,
      "time_str": "01:01.680",
      "text": "才会让你想离开",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 69.37,
      "time_str": "01:09.370",
      "text": "因为我不知道 下一辈子还是否能遇见你",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 76.52,
      "time_str": "01:16.520",
      "text": "所以我今生才会 那么努力把最好的给你",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 84.94,
      "time_str": "01:24.940",
      "text": "爱你都变成伤害你",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 88.56,
      "time_str": "01:28.560",
      "text": "我们的爱快要窒息",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 92.62,
      "time_str": "01:32.620",
      "text": "不是故意 只是太爱你",
